// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3188 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 322a2f40-700e-5caa-aa19-9c7000fa2e0d

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:12.04*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
